data.description: Classic home that is waiting for your touch. This rustic 4 bed, 2 bath home offers a unique floor plan and tons of historic charm! New roof installed this year. The home features a formal dining room with a fireplace, a spacious kitchen with plenty of cabinet space, and a living room that has a second fireplace. When you reach the top of the charming staircase, you will find the additional 3 bedrooms and another full bathroom. Brand new fenced rear yard with several fruit trees and large shade trees to provide plenty of fun. Property is currently unfurnished. Pictures may not reflect the current condition of the property.
